        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Dum in Dei nomine ...... coniunsemo nos <persName key="#Count #Assembly"
                            ref="#people/1257">Oddo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comes</rs> una cum <persName><name ref="Gariardus"
                                >Garurdo</name></persName> seo <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Teudaldus">Teodouldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs> et <persName key="#Monks"
                            >Ad...</persName>... <rs key="#Monks">monachis</rs> de <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Pigs #Fisheries #Animals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Monasteries #Monks #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47"><placeName ref="#places/15"
                                key="#Monasteries #Monks">Nonantola</placeName></orgName> ….
                            <persName key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Monasteries"
                            ref="#people/1258">Trasari</persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">advocatum</rs> suprascripto
                        monasterio, <rs key="#Curtes">corte</rs> domni regis in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Residential"
                            ref="#places/2981"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Residential"
                                ref="#estates/1136">Refere</geogName></placeName>, ubi <rs
                            key="#Assembly">nobiscum aderant</rs>
                        <persName key="#Local_elites #Scabini #Witness"><name ref="Podo"
                            >Pozo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Local_elites #Scabini"
                                ><name ref="Ermefredus">Ermefrit</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Local_elites #Scabini"><name ref="Robertus"
                                >Roteperte</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Local_elites #Scabini"><name ref="Madelbert"
                                >Madelberte</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scavinis</rs>, <rs key="#Local_elites">homines</rs>
                        Mantoanis, seo et <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Sesoerius"
                                >Sesoerius</name></persName> et <persName key="#Notary #Writer"
                                ><name ref="Arioald">Arioald</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, idem de <placeName
                            key="#Witness #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Notary #Local_elites #Scabini"
                            ref="#places/275">Mantoa</placeName>, nec non et homines <placeName
                            key="#Witness #Other_minor_officer #Scabini #Hay/fodder #Pigs #Fisheries #Animals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/1535">Flexisianis</placeName>, qui interfuerunt, idest
                            <persName key="#Scabini"><name ref="Frassimedus"
                            >Frassimedo</name></persName> scavino, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Laurentius">Laurencio</name></persName> filius quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Asterius">Asterio</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ihoannes">Iohani</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martini</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Iulianus">Iubianus</name></persName> gemelli,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Maurus">Maurus</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Silvanus">Silvano</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Other_minor_officer #Witness"><name ref="Senator"
                            >Senator</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_minor_officer">decano</rs>, simul et homines <placeName
                            key="#Witness #Scabini #Hay/fodder #Pigs #Fisheries #Animals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            ref="#places/1504">Solariensis</placeName>, idest <persName
                            key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Leontius">Lionnio</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Petronax"
                            >Petronaci</name></persName> germani scavinis, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Iulianus">Iulianus</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Duricius">Duricio</name></persName>. Adserevat in primis
                        Trasari advocatus ipsius monesteriis Nonantolas quia: 'Iste <persName
                            key="#Actionarii/actores" ref="#people/1259">Teotperte</persName>, qui
                        est <rs key="#Actionarii/actores">actor</rs> da <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >parte domno regis</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Pigs #Fisheries #Animals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Notary #Local_elites #Scabini"
                            ref="#estates/1137">corte Mantoana</geogName>, contendet nobis <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pascua</rs> …..sa est, seo decimas de <rs key="#Pigs"
                            >porcos</rs> adque <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >venacionem</rs> de <rs key="#Animals">feras</rs> quas nos ad parte
                        monasteriis Nonantulas legibus abere debemus medietatem in integrum, in
                        .........., que nuncopatur <placeName
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fisheries #Pigs #Animals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                            ref="#places/1589">Sarmetas</placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Hay/fodder #Fisheries #Pigs #Animals #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                            ref="#places/1588">Bondeno</placeName> et illa reliqua medietatem de
                        venacione in corte regis Mantoana'. Respondebat Teopertus actor, qui causa
                        ipsa da parte domni regis peragebat: 'Nescio quit vobis perteneant ad parte
                        monesteriis, sicut vos querites, nisi tantum scio quod vos abere debetes
                        medietatem de <rs key="#Fisheries">piscacionis</rs>, et partis domni regis
                        reliqua medietatem'. Iterum dicebat iam dictus Trasari advocatus
                        monasteriis: 'Ecce <rs key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">preceptoras</rs> regum
                        pre manibus abemus, <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >quod modo pars monesteriis medietatem de ipsas piscacionis et omni
                            qualiter superius diximus legibus abere debet</rs>'. Sic nos qui supra
                        Oddo comes preceptoras ipsas in nostris presencia ostendere et relegere
                        fecimus. Primis omnium ostendit nobis preceptum donacionis domni quondam
                            <persName ref="#people/48"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Emperor/king #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            >Aistulfo</persName> regis, deinde vero alio preceptum confirmacionis
                        domni quondam <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Emperor/king #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#people/249">Desiderio</persName> regis, tercio quidem preceptum
                        confirmacionis domni <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Emperor/king #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#people/14">Carolo</persName> inperatoris, adque eciam et quartum
                        preceptum domni <persName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Emperor/king #Imperial/royal_diploma"
                            ref="#people/118">Lodohic</persName> impeiratoris, ubi contenebatur
                        omnia quod modo pars monesteriis abere deberit per denotatas locas. Sicut
                        ipsas preceptoras donacionis et confermacionis in se contenebat, sic nos
                        predictus Oddo comes una cum in suprascriptis scavinis et auditores recte
                        paruiet esse et ita iudicavimus, ut pars suprascriptis monesteriis
                        Nonantolas abere debere secundum suas preceptoras omnia qualiter in eadem
                        preceptoras continebatur. Et ideo nos qui supra Oddo una cum suprascripto
                        Teutperto actore ipso Trasari advocato revistivimus ad parte suprascriptis
                        monesteriis Nonantulas de omnibus rebus, sicut in eorum preceptoras
                        contenetur. Finita est causa. Unde qualiter presentia nostri acta est causa
                        supradictus Arioald notarium nostrum <rs key="#Writer">scribere</rs>
                        precipimus. Facta noticiam iudicadi anno domno Lodohic inperatori quinto,
                        indicionem undecima. Signum + manus Oddoni comiti, qui hunc noticiam
                        iudicati fieri iusit. + Ego Pozo in his actis interfuit. + Ermefrit notarius
                        in his actis interfui. + Ego Roteperte in is hactis interfui. Signum + manus
                        Madelberto, qui in his actis <rs key="#Witness">interfui</rs>. + Ego
                        .......us in is actis interfui. + Ego .......ulmo in his actis interfui.
                        Signum + manus Lionnio, qui in his actis interfui. Signum + manus Petronaci,
                        qui in his actis interfui. Signum + manus Iuliano, qui interfui. Signum +
                        manus Iohanni, qui interfui. Signum + manus Senatoris, qui interfui. Signum
                        + manus Mauro, qui interfui. Signum + manus <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Iobus">Iobio</name></persName>, qui interfui. + Ego Laurencius
                        in is hactis interfui. + Ego Arioald notarius ex iussioni Oddoni comiti hun
                        noticiam iudicadi scripsi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
